snippet.title: Johnny Depp GIVEN ACCESS to Amber Heard's Phone To Prove Fake Abuse
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp GIVEN ACCESS to Amber Heard's Phone To Prove Fake Abuse


Hi there, and welcome back to Celebrity World! The court has given actor, Johnny Depp, access to his ex-wife, Amber Heard's, phone in high hopes that he will prove that she had faked her injuries he allegedly gave her. To know more about this story, then be sure to watch the full video. And don't forget to let us know your thoughts in the comments below. Thanks for watching.
